rows.label: tev061501_JNK0010
rows.name: Inquire[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev061501_SEL0011
rows.name: Ask about events since Lana came to New LA.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev061501_JNK0020
rows.name: Discuss[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev061501_SEL0021
rows.name: Ask Lana if anything is troubling her.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev061501_SEL0031
rows.name: Ask Lana what happened during the attack.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev061501_MSG0001
rows.name:
All of sudden Bubu insist on moving to New LA,
so here Lana is.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev061501_MSG0002
rows.name:
But expensive nopopotamus not grow on trees!
And living in city requires lot of investment.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev061501_MSG0003
rows.name:
Lana starting to worry about family finances.
Only way to get money is to work Bubu like slave...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev061501_MSG0004
rows.name:
Er, Lana mean that Bubu should work hard and invest
in future of family! Yes. That it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev061501_MSG0005
rows.name:
If friend know any good products to sell,
please tell Bubu, okay?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev061501_MSG0008
rows.name: Lana have more problems than are countable.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev061501_MSG0009
rows.name: But biggest problem is clingy husband, Bubu![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev061501_MSG0010
rows.name:
Everyone tell Lana that Bubu just worried about Lana...
That Bubu looooove Lana...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev061501_MSG0011
rows.name:
But Lana cannot even get alone time to go shopping,
or talk to friends, or even take bath![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev061501_MSG0012
rows.name:
Only comfort of Lana is sneaking off at night and
having secret talks with Walolo.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev061501_MSG0020
rows.name: Lana is mortified to say this, but...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev061501_MSG0021
rows.name:
right when Ganglion attacked and city was most in
danger...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev061501_MSG0022
rows.name:
husband Bubu try to offer friends money to become
bodyguard of Lana! Meeeeeh...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev061501_MSG0023
rows.name:
Now everyone in city probably think Lana is spoiled,
selfish Nopon.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev061501_MSG0024
rows.name: Sometimes Lana wish Bubu would jump off cliff![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev061501_MSG0025
rows.name:
...Er, by which Lana mean that dear Bubu should think
of everyone and not just Lana. Yes. That it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev061501_SEL1011
rows.name: Ask Lana about business.

rows.label: tev061501_SEL1021
rows.name: Ask Lana about recent developments.

rows.label: tev061501_MSG0026
rows.name:
Before, cuteness of Lana used to be like ball and chain
that kept Lana from living life of dreams.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev061501_MSG0027
rows.name: But then Lana realize cuteness is marketable![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev061501_MSG0028
rows.name:
Shake Lana's hand for just 100 credits!
Ruffle fur of Lana for just 10,000 credits!
Go for walk with Lana for just 1,000,000 credits![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev061501_MSG0029
rows.name: Lana going to work it big time and make major coin.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev061501_MSG0033
rows.name: Bubu is suddenly acting so manly and cool![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev061501_MSG0034
rows.name:
Lana always know that Bubu was better catch than
economically-challenged weakling like Walolo.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev061501_MSG0035
rows.name: Anyway, thanks for bringing Lana home to city, friend![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev061501_MSG0036
rows.name:
Lana is going to turn over new leaf and find happiness
here in New LA![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev061501_SEL2011
rows.name: Ask Lana about business.

rows.label: tev061501_SEL2021
rows.name: Ask Lana about recent developments.

rows.label: tev061501_MSG0037
rows.name:
Lana needs to think up some new products in order to
make living here.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev061501_MSG0038
rows.name:
...Aha! Human friends like small, round, fluffy things
like Nopon, right? Then Lana have great idea...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev061501_MSG0039
rows.name:
Lana will manufacture more of these and sell fake
littlepon to friends![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev061501_MSG0040
rows.name:
...Huh? Meh-meh! Lana mean stuffed animals that
LOOK like littlepon! Not that own littlepon is fake!
Do not get wrong idea.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev061501_MSG0044
rows.name: There, there. ...Whew! Raising littlepon is hard.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev061501_MSG0045
rows.name:
Can friend not see Lana is busy? Go make self
useful and tell Bubu that Lana say bye-bye![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev061501_MSG0046
rows.name:
Walolo will be taking care of Lana from now on.
Lana going to live in fast lane![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev061501_MSG0047
rows.name:
...Heh heh. Everything is going according to plan.
Lana finally free to do whatever Lana want![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev061501_MSG0048
rows.name: It is not fault of Lana that Lana so pretty...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev061501_MSG0049
rows.name:
Bubu need to stop suffocating Lana.
Lana wants to be free as soaring bird![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev061501_MSG0050
rows.name:
These secret talks with Walolo are only comfort for
poor Lana.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev061501_MSG0051
rows.name:
Lana knows that with Walolo around,
everything will be okay.[ST:wait ]
